<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <meta name="robots" content="noarchive">
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Successful</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: #F2F4F7;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #1A1F2E;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-header {
      background: #1B3A6B;
      padding: 28px 36px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .check-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: #2ECC71;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .check-icon svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      stroke: #fff;
      stroke-width: 3;
      fill: none;
    }

    .card-header-text h1 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .card-header-text p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 32px 36px;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .greeting strong {
      color: #1A1F2E;
    }

    .detail-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      background: #F8F9FB;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .detail-item label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #8A94A6;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .detail-item span {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1A1F2E;
    }

    .detail-item.highlight span {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1B3A6B;
    }

    .detail-item.full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .ref-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .ref-badge {
      flex: 1;
      background: #EEF2FF;
      border: 1px solid #C7D2FE;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
    }

    .ref-badge label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #6366F1;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .ref-badge span {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1A1F2E;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #EAEDF2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .footer-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .company-block {
      background: #F8F9FB;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #444;
    }

    .company-block strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1B3A6B;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .company-block a {
      color: #1B3A6B;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div class="check-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="card-header-text">
        <h1>Payment Successful</h1>
        <p>Your transaction has been processed</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="greeting">Dear <strong><%=pcSNAME%></strong>,<br>
      Your payment was successfully processed. Please keep this confirmation for your records.</p>

      <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item highlight full">
          <label>Amount Charged</label>
          <span>$<%=pcTRANSACTIONAMOUNT%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <label>Job Number</label>
          <span><%=pcDEPT%><%=pcORDNO%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <label>Payment Method</label>
          <span><%=pcTYPE%> ending in <%=RIGHT(pcACCOUNTNUM,4)%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <label>CARDHOLDER</label>
          <span><%=pcSJNAME%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <label>Date &amp; Time</label>
          <span><%=pcPAIDDTE%> ET</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ref-row">
        <div class="ref-badge">
          <label>Authorization Ref</label>
          <span><%=lcAUTHORIZE%></span>
        </div>
        <div class="ref-badge">
          <label>Transaction ID</label>
          <span><%=lcCTRANSNO%></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <p class="footer-note">Thank you for choosing <%=pcCOMPANY%>. If you have any questions about this charge, please contact us.</p>

      <div class="company-block">
        <strong><%=pcCOMPANY%></strong>
        <%=pcADD1%><br><%=pcADD2%><br>
        <a href="tel:<%=pcTOLLFREE%>"><%=pcTOLLFREE%></a><br>
        <a href="mailto:<%=pcOUREMAIL%>"><%=pcOUREMAIL%></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>